——这对于掌管中国陷入困境的股市的人来说是完美的形象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/firefighter-wu-becomes-chinas-market-regulator-after-rout-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：标准普尔 500 指数创历史新高 5,000 点，中国泄气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>Avolon首席执行官表示，波音公司“毫无疑问”在质量问题上取得了进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-undoubtedly-making-progress-quality-issues-avolon-ceo-says-2024-02-08/</link><description>全球第二大飞机租赁公司、波音主要客户 Avolon 的负责人周四表示，波音在解决质量问题方面“毫无疑问”取得了重大进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-undoubtedly-making-progress-quality-issues-avolon-ceo-says-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾感谢世界，解放军在新年贺词中展示模拟袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-thanks-world-pla-shows-simulated-attacks-new-years-messages-2024-02-08/</link><description>周四，蔡英文总统在农历新年致辞中感谢国际社会对台湾的支持。一天前，中国军方在模拟导弹袭击的图像中发布了一首敦促台湾“回家”的歌曲。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-thanks-world-pla-shows-simulated-attacks-new-years-messages-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国称领先的人工智能公司加入安全联盟以应对风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-says-leading-ai-companies-join-safety-consortium-address-risks-2024-02-08/</link><description>拜登政府周四表示，200 多家实体加入了一个新的美国财团，以支持生成式人工智能的安全开发和部署，其中包括领先的人工智能公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-says-leading-ai-companies-join-safety-consortium-address-risks-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>安赛乐米塔尔预计今年除中国以外的钢铁需求将增长3-4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-expects-3-4-steel-demand-growth-ex-china-this-year-2024-02-08/</link><description>全球第二大钢铁制造商安赛乐米塔尔周四表示，看到行业背景正在改善的初步迹象，预计今年中国以外的全球钢铁需求将增长 3-4%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 09:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-expects-3-4-steel-demand-growth-ex-china-this-year-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>一年过去了，一位中国明星交易撮合者的缺席给他的银行蒙上了一层阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</link><description>包凡被中国当局带走，此后同事就再也没有见过他。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 09:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>研究人员称，在华朝鲜工人中出现罕见的骚乱迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/signs-rare-unrest-among-north-korean-workers-china-researchers-say-2024-02-08/</link><description>韩国情报机构表示，朝鲜人在海外工作的恶劣条件导致了“事件和事故”，而研究人员报告称，中国一家与朝鲜军方有联系的贸易公司的工人在中国发生了罕见的抗议和骚乱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/signs-rare-unrest-among-north-korean-workers-china-researchers-say-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺、中国经济困境削弱信心，亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-robust-dollar-china-woes-dent-confidence-2024-02-08/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，对大多数亚洲货币的空头押注略有缓解，但仍坚定地处于看跌区域，原因是美国提前降息的希望减弱，使美元保持强劲，而区域强国中国的市场波动削弱了投资者信心。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-robust-dollar-china-woes-dent-confidence-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>1月份中国乘用车销量环比下降14.1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-passenger-vehicle-sales-fall-141-jan-mm-2024-02-08/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周四公布的数据显示，1月份中国乘用车销量环比下降14.1%，这是自8月份以来首次出现下滑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:14:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-passenger-vehicle-sales-fall-141-jan-mm-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行2月份将维持中期政策利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-set-stand-pat-medium-term-policy-rate-feb-2024-02-08/</link><description>路透调查显示，预计中国央行将在一周多后的时间内展期到期中期贷款时维持关键政策利率，因为当局似乎热衷于维持货币稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 05:44:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-set-stand-pat-medium-term-policy-rate-feb-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：中国通货紧缩忧虑新年凶兆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-08/</link><description>汤姆·威斯布鲁克 (Tom Westbrook) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 05:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>